      "date": "2014-04-09 15:56:02.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nYes the patch is needed for RHEL6.3/64 but currently you can't build either since when RHEL6.5 support was added the support for earlier RHEL kerrnels were removed from the kernel patch series.",
